                    <span>Milestones is a great, indepth biography on possibly the most important and influential Jazzman of all time.  This book not only showcases Miles life as a musician, but also gives a histroy lesson as to what was  happening to the Jazz world.  For any Jazz lover...this book is a must!</span>
                  
              
